title: [Biology] Hepatitis C Virus Drugs That Inhibit the SARS-CoV-2 Papain-Like Protease Synergize with Remdesivir to Suppress Viral Replication in Cell Culture

[Medicine] Ginkgo biloba extract contains naturally occurring inhibitors against SARS-CoV-2. Findings suggest that bioflavonoids could act as promising lead compounds to develop anti-SARS-CoV-2 agents. The compound can also become a lead ingredient in anti-coronavirus drugs to prevent future outbreaks.
